snippet.title: DoctorTale -- Teaser (UnderEvent 23)
snippet.description:
"The Doctor discovers that several important planets have disappeared without a trace. This threatens an intergalactic crisis and possible conflicts. It is up to the Doctor to go in search of the lost systems and discover something more than she could have originally imagined."

This teaser-trailer was produced for @UNDEREVENT 2023 and introduced in the Special Mentions category. The content of the video is made by OUTTERS, music by MatthewNova.
